{"tid":814030,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"感情做錯個方係唔係就冇資格傷心","createTime":"2018-09-11T02:05:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T04:11:41.000Z","uid":204545,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8af93d0dcfa67c114cf5add0b614559f1826c60a","tid":814030,"uid":204545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T02:05:08.000Z","msg":"由初中已經一齊一齊左幾年<br />\n貪玩貪新鮮同咗第二個一齊<br />\n之後被發現 佢都原諒咗我<br />\n但其實每次嗌交佢地會講翻件事<br />\n但最後佢都頂唔順同我講分手<br />\n到講分手我先明白自己好愛佢<br />\n分手一個月有新女<br />\n我係唔係冇資格唔開心<br />\n分左手半年以為放低咗但每次有人講起都會好sad<br />\n吾開心要收埋因爲全世界都知你係仆街<br />\n我都知係自己一手造成<br />\n純粹發洩下因爲冇人好講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf11310e33e0ef8b1ec88760c2800464315f3e1","tid":814030,"uid":17502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T02:08:47.000Z","msg":"無資格，但你個case都無需要。<br />\n<br />\nbtw，死返5p。"},{"pid":"30037528e2db0dad69882d4fbab65014341d3e4c","tid":814030,"uid":208364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T02:12:41.000Z","msg":"你由做個一刻，你就唔愛你女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cfba8ac8d1d33bd6fcfceab13cf4e223ca4e523","tid":814030,"uid":131725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T02:22:41.000Z","msg":"貪新鮮既根本就無資格學人講傷心<br />\n收皮"},{"pid":"b42e94e12651645c7fe6055e63323c485bbca9aa","tid":814030,"uid":91230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T02:24:13.000Z","msg":"吾你老母"},{"pid":"acc67a9438d705fd5eef9b1c836dddd417e7dd59","tid":814030,"uid":29312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T02:59:12.000Z","msg":"係,吾你老母"},{"pid":"301658b5fe15f5294ac2ad7ea6c7a40435c3e5fc","tid":814030,"uid":190604,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTi